  {
    "id": 8833591115836,
    "title": "2mm Full",
    "handle": "2mm-full",
    "body_html": "<div>Our <strong>2mm Full</strong> is made with the best wetsuit material available—100% Yamamoto Neoprene. This model is one of the favorite suits worn by all the pro surfers who've tested our products, including some of the best surfers on the Vans Surf Team :)</div>\n<p></p><div>Designed and tested by Alex &amp; Buzz at Ocean Beach, San Francisco—FERAL is built to last seasons, not sessions. Best for 59-69 degree water <em>(temperature range dependent on personal burliness)</em>.</div>",
