  {
    "id": 6939047231548,
    "title": "4'10\" Disorder (Used)",
    "handle": "410-disorder-used",
    "body_html": "<p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>Regular Foot</strong></span></p>\n<p><meta charset=\"utf-8\"><span data-mce-fragment=\"1\">This is the pinnacle of all of our research and development of performance asym surfcraft over the last decade. The next generation of the proven </span><a href=\"https://albumsurf.com/collections/disasym\" title=\"Disasym\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\" data-mce-href=\"https://albumsurf.com/collections/disasym\" target=\"_blank\">Disasym</a><span data-mce-fragment=\"1\">. Set up for regular- or goofy-foot. Twin-fin speed on your toes with quad grip and a pulled-in rail line on your heels, and now with an updated performance rocker that opens up more in smaller waves. The deep single concave that rolls to a vee through the fins allows this board to light up wherever you go. Enjoy the speed of a twin fin married to the maneuverability of a shortboard. Goes equally well frontside and backside, designed to maximize each approach uniquely.  Ride it 2-5” shorter than your normal shortboard and at your standard volume.</span></p>",
